SOURCE

Online article on Engadget https://www.engadget.com/2017/06/27/microsoft-sports-performance-platform/

AGENT

Microsoft

GOAL

To help teams track and improve player behavior in sports.

DATA

Athlete statistics, team statistics on wins and losses, etc.

METHODS

Big data manipulation with machine learning.

RESULTS

It is an experimental project for Microsoft. The company looks for sports organizations to be a part of the project. The ultimate goal is to use machine learning to help improve teams in sports.

COMMENTS

This is a good example of using machine learning in sports. It would be great to use classifying algorithms to determine if a player is at risk of injury during play. This may save money and time for players and organizations.

